{"id":45662,"date":"2024-01-19T09:46:00","date_gmt":"2024-01-19T04:16:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=45662"},"modified":"2024-02-20T18:49:16","modified_gmt":"2024-02-20T13:19:16","slug":"11-smart-kitchen-designs","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/11-smart-kitchen-designs\/","title":{"rendered":"11 Smart Kitchen Designs: The Future of Home Decor"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Enjoy a seamless cooking experience with these smart kitchen design ideas.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>What is a smart kitchen design? When the makers of German modular kitchens superseded <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/italian-kitchen-designs\/\">Italian kitchens<\/a>, they built a road in the high-end segment for homeowners in India. Today, when it comes to futuristic kitchen concepts, there are many options in the market. A hub of the house where you spend solid hours of your day, the idea behind smart kitchen designs is to reduce daily workload.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>But do you need one? Does it save space without compromising on style or does it make everyday cooking a breeze? A smart kitchen <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">interior design<\/a> provides everything you need to make cooking, cleaning, and storage effective. Integrated with state-of-the-art technology conceptualised to fit homes of different sizes, smart kitchens will be a key trend in 2024.\u00a0<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here we discuss 11 smart kitchen designs, what they offer, and the right one for your home.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">U Shaped Smart Kitchen Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Let\u2019s take a minute to appreciate this simple yet smart kitchen design for small homes. Featuring a breathable U-shaped design with space for built-in kitchen appliances, you have so much more room to get the prep done. The idea of sleek white custom cabinets adds an aesthetic value to the space and frees up drawers for everyday cutlery.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222211\/u-shaped-smart-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"U shaped smart kitchen design with white custom cabinets adds an aesthetic value\" class=\"wp-image-45673\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222211\/u-shaped-smart-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222211\/u-shaped-smart-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222211\/u-shaped-smart-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222211\/u-shaped-smart-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">U-shaped kitchen design is a smart move to maximise space<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">L Shaped Smart Kitchen Cabinet Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A modern smart <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/modular-kitchen-design\/\">kitchen design<\/a> saves space and provides a cohesive look to your home. This L-shaped modular kitchen design works by allowing a seamless and logical flow between the stove and kitchen island. You can enjoy a quick breakfast, use it as a buffet stand for parties, and as a segregator between the kitchen and living room!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222205\/l-shaped-smart-kitchen-design.jpg\" alt=\"L shaped smart kitchen cabinet design that provides a cohesive look\" class=\"wp-image-45672\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222205\/l-shaped-smart-kitchen-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222205\/l-shaped-smart-kitchen-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222205\/l-shaped-smart-kitchen-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222205\/l-shaped-smart-kitchen-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">The use of wood with black granite adds finesse to the space. <\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Modular kitchen interiors that saves upto 20% space\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/08172146\/modular-kitchen-interiors-that-saves-upto-20-percentage-space.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Floating Cabinets For A Smart Kitchen<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another interesting use of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/modern-l-shaped-kitchen\/\">L-shaped modular kitchen design<\/a> is the strategic use of floating cabinets. Built to hold exclusive cutlery and appliances like your microwave, the design makes cleaning counters easy. A laminate paired with white and teal matches the drawers below to give the space a minimal but chic vibe.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222200\/smart-kitchen-design-with-floating-cabinets.jpg\" alt=\"White and light blue smart Kitchen with floating cabinets elevates the space look\" class=\"wp-image-45671\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222200\/smart-kitchen-design-with-floating-cabinets.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/