 this innovative design, perfect for Indian homes. Every inch of the kitchen is strategically organised with space for built-in appliances, push cutlery cabinets and grocery storage.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222148\/smart-kitchen-design-with-built-in-appliances.jpg\" alt=\"Modern smart kitchen design with built-in appliances\" class=\"wp-image-45669\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222148\/smart-kitchen-design-with-built-in-appliances.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222148\/smart-kitchen-design-with-built-in-appliances-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222148\/smart-kitchen-design-with-built-in-appliances-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222148\/smart-kitchen-design-with-built-in-appliances-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Have a seamless cooking experience with this design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Movable Island In A Smart Kitchen Design&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Checking all the boxes of a smart kitchen design is this dual-purpose island, and for good reason. It keeps the space neat without compromising functionality. Plus, since it has wheels, you can use it as a table and as a storage box!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full is-resized\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222142\/smart-kitchen-design-with-a-movable-island.jpg\" alt=\"Open smart kitchen design with a movable island\" class=\"wp-image-45668\" style=\"width:840px;height:504px\" width=\"840\" height=\"504\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\