designer about the importance of space, and they\u2019ll show you this kitchen design. The vibe of this kitchen is the perfect mix of elegance and functionality. Sleek push-glass cabinets lend a modern approach to storing dinner sets. While the idea behind a built-in sink is to keep the washing area clean and stain-free.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222122\/smart-kitchen-design-approach.jpg\" alt=\"Smart kitchen with plush-glass cabinets\" class=\"wp-image-45665\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222122\/smart-kitchen-design-approach.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222122\/smart-kitchen-design-approach-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222122\/smart-kitchen-design-approach-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222122\/smart-kitchen-design-approach-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Natural finish wood and spotted backsplash add a stylish touch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Open Smart Kitchen Design Layout&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Another brilliant idea when designing a smart kitchen is to play with all the space you have. An out-of-the-box design, this gorgeous kitchen is curated for seamless movement while cooking. The custom cabinet with room for an OTG and its utensils adds an ultra-luxe feel without effort.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/05\/19222117\/open-smart-kitchen-design-layout.jpg\" alt=\"Open smart kitchen design layout with horizontal shelves\" class=\"wp-image-45664\" srcset=\"https: